Visit projectsite from *martinchodev* OK Diaspora Native WebApp First of all: I am not a developer. I understand a few basics and most of my work is done by copy and paste. This app is build from the original *DiasporaNativeWebApp* Version 1.6.1 from *martinchodev*, which is released under the GPL-license. Because I wanted a better visual integration with my personal phone-setup, I changed a few icons and the splashscreen. I also added the navigationdrawer and the floating-action-buttons. I also did some minor changes. Nearly all of my changes are tagged with "By_me" in my sourcecode. All of the rest is the work of *martinchodev*. Big thanks to him.
